It consists  of a client -side R package ( https://github.com/stefan -m-lenz/dsBoltzmannMachines ) and a  server -side R  package that can be installed in an Opal server and called from the client -side  (https://github.com/stefan -m-lenz/dsBoltzmannMachines Client ).
